<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd" []>
<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-document-content-rendering-preferences" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying Content Rendering Preferences</title>
  <conbody id="body">
    <p>In general, <xref href="content-rendering.xml">content rendering</xref> depends on the current <xref href="document-type.xml">document type</xref>.</p>
    <p>However, you can  specify some preferences that will control the view of documents of all types.  These document content rendering preferences include the following:<ol>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-context-hints-settings.xml">The behaviour of context hints</xref>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-large-document-folding-rules.xml">Large document folding parameters</xref>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-tag-style.xml">Representation details of Markup tags</xref>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-document-background-color.xml">Background color of documents</xref>.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-nbsp-rendering.xml">The view of NBSP symbols</xref>.</p>
        </li>
      </ol></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
